description:
IDE for data analysts and analytics engineers

JetBrains DataSpell is an IDE for data analysis with Jupyter notebooks and SQL-cells, interactive Python scripts, dbt Core, SQL databases support, and low-code features.
- JetBrains Data Wrangler for simplifying data cleaning and preparation
- R version 4.4, enhancing the coding experience with improved language features
Visit our What's New page to learn about all the new features.
